# Supabase Configuration (Optional - for cloud database)
# If you want to use Supabase instead of localStorage, add these variables in Vercel dashboard

# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

# Example:
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://xyzcompany.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# Note: 
# - Without these variables, the app will use localStorage (works perfectly offline)
# - With these variables, the app will use Supabase + localStorage hybrid mode
# - Add these in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables